Cherry blossom soufflé

02:17.049 --> 02:20.488
or bittersweet chocolate?

02:22.011 --> 02:24.927
- Or, better idea...

02:26.233 --> 02:27.408
- We'll have one of
everything.

02:27.451 --> 02:29.192
Every dessert on the menu.
And coffee.

02:29.236 --> 02:31.238
Decaf for the lady.

02:31.281 --> 02:32.630
- Very good, sir.

02:32.674 --> 02:34.023
- Thank you.

02:34.066 --> 02:36.547
