02:36.591 --> 02:39.246
- I have something
to ask you.

02:40.421 --> 02:43.685
A commitment I have
never made before.

02:52.520 --> 02:55.523
- When I said I was happy...
- Just hear me out.

02:57.046 --> 03:00.223
Amanda Rollins, will you...

03:00.267 --> 03:01.703
Go ahead.

03:08.971 --> 03:09.972
- It's a key.

03:14.324 --> 03:16.152
- I was in awe of you.

03:16.196 --> 03:17.414
Between that rising fastball,

03:17.458 --> 03:18.850
your curveball, your change up,

03:18.894 --> 03:21.026
and the fact that you could
swing a bat too.

03:21.070 --> 03:22.854
I mean, for a pitcher.

03:22.898 --> 03:25.335
Oh, gee, thanks.

03:25.379 --> 03:27.207
Hey, do you, do you want
another one?

03:27.250 --> 03:28.512
- Yeah, I do.

03:28.556 --> 03:31.254
- Yeah.
- Okay, I'll be right back.

03:34.823 --> 03:41.873
