do you?

04:02.242 --> 04:03.634
- No, I don't,

04:03.678 --> 04:06.376
I don't, I really,
I really don't.

04:08.509 --> 04:11.338
- You raped me,
you son of a bitch.

04:22.784 --> 04:29.791
