05:12.703 --> 05:14.966
- Good morning.

05:15.010 --> 05:17.665
- Hey. Thanks.

05:22.844 --> 05:24.019
Nice place.

05:24.062 --> 05:26.326
- Do you even remember
how you got here?

05:26.369 --> 05:27.414
- Barely.

05:27.457 --> 05:29.198
Oh, I must have been

05:29.241 --> 05:30.199
