05:30.242 --> 05:31.418
- Oh, yeah.

05:31.461 --> 05:32.636
You were messed up.

05:32.680 --> 05:34.116
What happened last night?

05:35.509 --> 05:38.773
- You said you were accused
of rape.

05:43.212 --> 05:45.170
- I, uh...

05:45.214 --> 05:47.129
I ran into a woman.

05:48.826 --> 05:51.307
