at first.

05:51.351 --> 05:52.700
She, uh...

05:52.743 --> 05:56.443
She looked at me
like she'd seen a ghost.

05:56.486 --> 05:58.358
And then she hauled off
and hit me.

05:58.401 --> 06:00.011
Accused me of assaulting her.

06:01.317 --> 06:03.363
- No.

06:03.406 --> 06:04.668
12 years ago

06:04.712 --> 06:08.455
it was a, a late season game
against the Mets.

06:08.498 --> 06:12.023
And a few of the guys decided
to go to a bar after.

06:12.067 --> 06:14.548
There was this--
there was this woman there.

06:14.591 --> 06:17.246
- Right.

06:17.289 --> 06:20.597
I was drunk.
We all were.

06:20.641 --> 06:24.427
A few of us decided to go
back to my hotel room.

06:24.471 --> 06:26.908
Things got a little crazy.

06:26.951 --> 06:28.431
I remember

06:28.475 --> 06:30.390
