and then...

06:33.436 --> 06:34.872
I woke up.

06:34.916 --> 06:37.701
In my bed, alone.
Everyone was gone.

06:41.401 --> 06:44.360
- I called her the next day
and she...

06:44.404 --> 06:47.363
she said...

06:47.407 --> 06:49.104
"Try to talk to me again

06:49.147 --> 06:50.453
and I'm going to the police."

06:51.759 --> 06:54.936
- No, I was never contacted.

06:54.979 --> 06:57.025
- Okay.

06:57.068 --> 06:59.506
You're telling me
that you were drinking.

06:59.549 --> 07:00.594
You were acting crazy.

07:00.637 --> 07:01.682
All right, you sure this

07:01.725 --> 07:02.639
