07:02.683 --> 07:03.640
You're not lying to me?

07:03.684 --> 07:04.902
Don't lie to me, man.

07:04.946 --> 07:06.251
- I'm not.
- Tell me the truth.

07:06.295 --> 07:07.252
- I am telling you the truth.

07:07.296 --> 07:09.037
I'm not lying to you.

07:10.560 --> 07:12.910
I might not
remember everything

07:12.954 --> 07:17.175
but I know I didn't
rape anyone.

07:20.352 --> 07:21.484
I need to talk to her.

07:21.528 --> 07:23.573
Find out what the hell's
going on.

07:23.617 --> 07:25.575
- Alicia, your statement
was very helpful.

07:25.619 --> 07:27.229
- I still can't remember
much about that night.

07:27.272 --> 07:29.274
I mean, I've tried, but--
- Sometimes our memory

07:29.318 --> 07:30.580
comes back in bits and pieces.

07:30.624 --> 07:31.929
- Sometimes not at all.

07:31.973 --> 07:33.540
- But this still goes
to trial--

07:33.583 --> 07:35.106
- Yes, we know from your
blood alcohol content

07:35.150 --> 07:36.934
