07:49.294 --> 07:52.646
Anything that shows that
she was incapacitated.

07:55.518 --> 07:56.780
- There he is.

07:56.824 --> 08:00.392
- Oh, look who the cat
dragged in!

08:00.436 --> 08:01.742
Oh, man!

08:01.785 --> 08:02.960
- Hey, Reggie, long time.
How are you?

08:03.004 --> 08:04.048
- Man, too long.

08:04.092 --> 08:05.833
