08:08.879 --> 08:10.402
- No, we've been
keeping him busy.

08:10.446 --> 08:12.317
Detective Tutuola, NYPD.

08:12.361 --> 08:14.537
- Whoa, wait, I'm not
in some kind of trouble, am I?

08:14.581 --> 08:16.104
- No, no, not at all.

08:16.147 --> 08:17.322
