08:20.064 --> 08:21.631
- Oh, hey, can I--
can I get you guys something?

08:21.675 --> 08:24.068
- No, I'm okay.

08:24.112 --> 08:27.855
So...do you remember
August, 2006?

08:27.898 --> 08:30.771
I had a no-hitter going until
you stepped up to the plate?

08:30.814 --> 08:31.946
- We had some fun that night.

08:31.989 --> 08:33.208
- Yeah, actually, that's what

08:33.251 --> 08:34.426
