08:34.470 --> 08:35.645
- We're trying to locate
a woman

08:35.689 --> 08:37.821
that came to the bar
after that game.

08:37.865 --> 08:40.998
- She was blonde and I think
her name was Sarah.

08:41.042 --> 08:43.566
You and me, we were talking
with her and a friend of hers.

08:43.610 --> 08:45.699
Big brown eyes, legs for days.

08:45.742 --> 08:47.004
- Went back to your hotel room,

08:47.048 --> 08:49.006
had a couple of fifths
of Silver Patron,

08:49.050 --> 08:50.834
Dom Perignon.

08:50.878 --> 08:52.183
