08:52.227 --> 08:54.621
- Right, so you do remember.

08:54.664 --> 08:57.841
- I remember everything.

08:57.885 --> 08:59.539
Here, come on.
I'll show you.

09:04.413 --> 09:07.285
Big brown eyes?
I married her.

09:07.329 --> 09:08.765
Wanda.
We got two kids.

09:08.809 --> 09:10.375
And yes, in case
you're wondering,

09:10.419 --> 09:12.029
