10:26.321 --> 10:26.495
.

10:26.538 --> 10:28.584
- Hey, I'm going to the deli.
You want anything?

10:28.628 --> 10:29.803
- No, I'm good.

10:29.846 --> 10:31.282
- All right.
Steak for lunch, huh?

10:31.326 --> 10:32.849
I guess you are good.

10:32.893 --> 10:34.242
- It was leftovers.

10:34.285 --> 10:36.374
Al always over-orders.

10:36.418 --> 10:38.376
