pretty loosely here.

10:41.292 --> 10:43.947
- He asked me to move in
with him.

10:45.296 --> 10:47.168
- Well, I hope
you told him no.

10:47.211 --> 10:48.604
- I told him that
I'd think about it.

10:48.648 --> 10:50.127
What, you're telling me

10:50.171 --> 10:52.042
