apartment.

11:06.927 --> 11:08.058
- No.

11:08.102 --> 11:09.494
- No, I'm just--
you know what,

11:09.538 --> 11:11.540
if I wanted
a "why buy the cow" speech

11:11.583 --> 11:12.628
I'd call my mother.

11:12.672 --> 11:13.890
- You know, Rollins,
I'm just saying

11:13.934 --> 11:15.109
that you deserve to be happy.

11:15.152 --> 11:16.719
You deserve to be
taken care of.

11:16.763 --> 11:18.068
- And Al takes care of me.

11:18.112 --> 11:20.157
- No he doesn't.
Look, there is a difference

11:20.201 --> 11:21.768
