11:23.508 --> 11:24.945
- I'll believe that
when I see it.

11:24.988 --> 11:26.686
- Okay.

11:26.729 --> 11:28.644
- Hey, I'm gonna get you
a ginger ale, all right?

11:28.688 --> 11:31.603
