with an opening statement.

11:36.260 --> 11:37.740
- Soon.
You'll be great.

11:37.784 --> 11:39.655
- You know, we have a room
that you can wait in.

11:39.699 --> 11:41.222
- All right, come with me.
- Okay.

11:41.265 --> 11:42.353
- Thanks, Carmen.

11:42.397 --> 11:43.485
You prepped her testimony?

11:43.528 --> 11:45.182
- Yeah, backwards
and forwards.

11:45.226 --> 11:46.183
- You think she'll do
all right on the stand?

11:46.227 --> 11:47.402
- Well, I hope so.

11:47.445 --> 11:48.577
There's a lot
she doesn't remember.

11:48.620 --> 11:50.013
