this all up?

11:59.022 --> 12:00.763
Because what woman
wouldn't want to go

12:00.807 --> 12:03.244
through the trauma
of a rape investigation,

12:03.287 --> 12:05.725
a trial, just for kicks?

12:07.901 --> 12:10.033
He's guilty, Peter.

12:13.080 --> 12:14.951
Are you okay?

12:14.995 --> 12:16.257
- Yeah.

12:16.300 --> 12:19.216
Yeah, I'm fine.
Just trouble sleeping.

12:25.527 --> 12:27.703
- I got to the bar around 11:30

12:27.747 --> 12:29.313
and then the last thing
I remember,

12:29.357 --> 12:31.925
Roger Madden walked me home.

12:31.968 --> 12:33.883
I said I didn't
need help but

12:33.927 --> 12:35.145
he didn't listen.

12:36.277 --> 12:38.279
- I woke up the next morning.

12:38.322 --> 12:39.802
