12:42.196 --> 12:43.980
- I went to the hospital.

12:44.024 --> 12:45.677
For a rape kit.

12:45.721 --> 12:47.244
The nurse called SVU.

12:47.288 --> 12:48.855
The detective said
I'd been assaulted.

12:48.898 --> 12:52.075
- But you never completely
remembered the assault itself?

12:52.119 --> 12:54.251
- No.

12:54.295 --> 12:56.688
I do remember telling him
earlier that evening

12:56.732 --> 12:58.560
that I didn't want
to go home with him.

12:58.603 --> 13:00.867
- You let me buy you drinks
all night.

13:00.910 --> 13:02.433
- Mr. Madden, that's enough.

13:02.477 --> 13:05.045
One more outburst,
I will hold you in contempt.

13:05.088 --> 13:06.568
- I apologize, Your Honor.

13:06.611 --> 13:08.222
- Mr. Stone.
- Your Honor.

13:08.265 --> 13:10.050
Please continue, Ms. Beck.

13:10.093 --> 13:12.356
- I didn't want
to go home with him.

13:13.705 --> 13:17.448
I would have never
consented to sex.

13:17.492 --> 13:18.667
Never.

13:21.104 --> 13:22.627
- Thank you, Ms. Beck.

13:25.108 --> 13:26.196
- Earlier that evening,

13:26.240 --> 13:27.241
did you consent

13:27.284 --> 13:28.590
to have a drink with my client?

13:28.633 --> 13:29.460
- Yes.

13:29.504 --> 13:30.592
- Did you consent to having

13:30.635 --> 13:31.854
several drinks with my client

13:31.898 --> 13:33.725
while flirting with him for,

13:33.769 --> 13:35.553
according to the bartender,
over an hour?

13:35.597 --> 13:37.860
- Yes, but I didn't--
- Yes, but what, you...

13:37.904 --> 13:40.602
remember consenting to have
drinks with my client

13:40.645 --> 13:42.909
but you don't remember
consenting to the sex?

13:42.952 --> 13:45.085
- Objection.
- Overruled.

13:45.128 --> 13:46.738
- I'm not making this up.

13:46.782 --> 13:49.045
I wouldn't be sitting here
if I wasn't raped.

13:49.089 --> 13:50.481
- We just heard you testify

13:50.525 --> 13:52.309
that you don't remember
what happened

13:52.353 --> 13:55.791
between walking home
and waking up.

13:55.835 --> 13:56.923
You could have consented

13:56.966 --> 13:59.490
and not remember
that you consented.

14:02.015 --> 14:04.452
- You tell me.

14:04.495 --> 14:07.063
- Roger Madden raped me.

14:07.107 --> 14:08.848
I'm only here because I believe

14:08.891 --> 14:13.809
if I can face the man
who raped me,

14:13.853 --> 14:15.376
if I can get justice,

14:15.419 --> 14:17.857
I'll somehow get my life back.

14:30.870 --> 14:32.045
- Peter.
- Hey.

14:35.439 --> 14:37.006
- Uh, sure, come in.

14:37.050 --> 14:38.529
- Thanks.

14:40.314 --> 14:41.750
- Look, I'm just gonna

14:41.793 --> 14:43.186
come out and say it.

14:43.230 --> 14:45.667
I've been accused
of sexual assault.

14:48.888 --> 14:50.715
- It was 12 years ago.

14:50.759 --> 14:53.066
I was drunk.

14:53.109 --> 14:55.155
Look, but I know

14:55.198 --> 14:56.504
in my bones

14:56.547 --> 14:58.201
in my heart and in my soul

14:58.245 --> 15:00.160
I didn't rape this woman.

15:00.203 --> 15:02.684
- But she says you did.

15:02.727 --> 15:04.077
Why?

15:04.120 --> 15:05.774
- I don't know.

15:05.817 --> 15:07.123
What I do know

15:07.167 --> 15:08.168
is no matter how drunk I was,

15:08.211 --> 15:09.909
